# Academic release: track only the training entrypoint, argument/data/model wiring,
# and the qignn package. All other top-level files (analysis, baselines, shell runners,
# etc.) stay untracked—keep them locally as needed.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/requirements.txt
!/train.py
!/model_factory.py
!/qignn
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.eggs/
*.egg-info/
/data/
/results/
